Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Formerly served in the French Foreign Legion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when freelance and fought in Nicaragua in 1979
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,From 1981 to 1984 assisted the Guerrilla rebels in Afghanistan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in 1987 you played a key role in the assassination of radical Islamic leaders in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.49,0:01:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Top secret moussard operation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite an impressive resume I must admit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it Mr Hugo Bernhard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt that a mercenary of your caliber must be quite a teacher and I'm sure a number of distinguished
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Men must have been under your instruction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a good idea to send some of our own officers to attend your seminar and have you with them into shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be great
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this man here a good student by any chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe he showed up at your training grounds about 5 months ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that he is a genius with a scalpel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm wondering about is whether he has any Talent with a gun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't divulge information about my pupils to anyone period
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So have you ever trained with a gun before
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No I guess that means that you're self taught then
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never shot a gun before
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What you mean not even once right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm asking for the impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt said you're my only hope right now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I make all my students forget everything they learned before they got here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I'll be teaching someone who's never shot a gun before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump rope
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of your experience or lack of this is where everyone starts now jump like that child over there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well get started yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster now hurry it up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I said faster
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Balance it's all about balance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on faster
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I said faster
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well obviously I can't jump rope nearly as well as you do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me something is this what you do you know always supervising student training like this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right I understand you don't have to keep on staring at me like that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey it's a branding
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's looking for food for its chicks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong are you too tired to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't train if you pass out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She your daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or your granddaughter Maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That little girl is the daughter of a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut her down right before very
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Backing me on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,On Mission in the jungle I ran into a hut
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And there she was with her mother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd have been a fraction of a second slower it would have been me that died that day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the child back here with me I couldn't just leave her
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,From that moment on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't smiled once
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably hate me for the rest of her life
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the sort of thing that happens when you have a gun
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you can't handle that then I'd suggest you don't carry one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What a person sometimes it smells just like Daphne blossoms
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right that's enough of that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So then
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for some more running
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away then
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're done running come to the bottom of the hill in the back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's down there the firing range
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The firing range
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Two shots
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to make sure that whenever you fire your gun you always pull the trigger twice if you can do that instinctively it better is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Chances of taking out your objective
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're as good as Dad it's all over
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always preparing meals for me so I thought it would cook for you today it's a Japanese stew of meat and potatoes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called nicujaga go on dig in I think you'll both enjoy it those are chopstick
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're carved out of wood I made them I thought it would make our dining experience more authentic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really good at using Chopsticks aren't you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Again faster
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it again
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a baby brambling
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it fell out of its nest
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No wait you have to put it back
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That chick is going to die
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult to raise them like that they rarely survive for that long outside of the nest
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put it back
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Back with its mother okay
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,3 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the time you've got
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Find your target and pull the trigger cuz one mistake of the slightest bit of hesitation and you're dead
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me how well did he perform over those 5 months he was there training with you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically speaking he was a perfect student
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He built up the necessary stamina
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And his concentration while firing was extraordinary
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to actually shoot a person is another story
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether or not he is successful on his first kill
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it all comes down to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Either he's got what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Already
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I see
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder which road this man will choose
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it matters not
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea where he might have gone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you do know where I would really like for you to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all you've done for me over the past 5 months
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the remaining tuition I owe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And please help yourself to the necojaga
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Again
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about it you do know where this man was heading don't you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That I can't tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine you can go now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This way sir
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One man have a ball
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second where's the Cherry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a Manhattan without the Cherry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah my mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let it slide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Business always goes well when I'm sucking on one of these
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A lucky charm is a lucky charm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to Papa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope there's still something of value we're taking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.47,0:22:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well well look at what we've got here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a five finger free for all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if there's anything valuable enough for a connoisseur like Auto Hackle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know what's going to happen first year issue in Canada for governor next thing you and your
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't get shot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,LOL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Down to business
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.07,0:23:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing this is where they kept the safe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I getting a chill this is creepy as hell I've never felt anything like this could
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Could somebody be in there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I so scared about it ain't like me to be a chicken move
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands behind your head
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man I can't believe this damn bartender at his fault
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgot the Cherry
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I said put your hands up all right all right all right give me a break on this one officer I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking anything yet I promise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a cop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.20,0:23:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're robbing the place too huh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.25,0:23:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well in that case why don't you just put that thing away and we'll have ourselves behind your head now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.14,0:24:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,James what's with this guy's a bigger boy scout than the freaking cops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidding me thanks for nothing buddy come out of here don't follow me someone like you just
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the way you call me down
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.74,0:24:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right I thought I recognized you you're all over the papers you're the doctor wanted for questioning
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.14,0:24:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning connection with councilman Springs Missouri are you a thief
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.54,0:24:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go around killing people you wouldn't know anything about the murders that happened in that house would you no idea so get out of my
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.94,0:24:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Face will you later
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.34,0:24:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey doctor you're some sort of top notch surgeon aren't you my brilliant
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.74,0:24:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Changes came up with a fantastic idea do you think that people meet by chance doctor they don't
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.14,0:25:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me I know I believe in fate I think people meet for a reason and my gut tells me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.54,0:25:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Destined to become Partners call me crazy but I think a lot of folks in the underground
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.94,0:25:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he need someone like you you know guys who need to hide out so they can't go to regular doctors for help
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.34,0:25:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen you leave the management to Old Heckle here I'll make you the world's best underground doctor in no time I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.74,0:25:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be a millionaire before you know it hey hey
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.14,0:25:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you're going there's something I have to do and it can't wait well I'd hold my
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.54,0:25:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is if I were you you want to know about the murders in that house don't you well I guess you'd like to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.94,0:25:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that I saw the killer am I right what did you say are you telling me the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know what's the Killer Blonde and about 20 years of age
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.74,0:26:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind you just tell me about who you saw there team up with me and I'd be happy to doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.42,0:26:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the third floor
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.98,0:26:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So how did you come to know all of this anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.28,0:26:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent a month checking out the councilman's house case in the joint I do my homework just when I'm ready to make a move
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.68,0:26:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer beats me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.96,0:26:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minutes later I look in the window and they're dead worm food
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.80,0:26:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I figured I might be able to Blackmail the murderer so I followed him here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.66,0:26:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all you really need to prove your innocence doc know what I'm saying all you have to do is call the police and tell him
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.32,0:26:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After that we should go somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.11,0:26:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down relax talk over a drink about our future together as partners hey
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.77,0:26:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop what are you doing what do you want to talk to him for what did you miss the part where he murders people
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.91,0:26:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Man what is he thinking looking for trouble like that I'm out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.82,0:26:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.10,0:26:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A cash cow like him is a rare opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.94,0:27:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn I usually make it a rule not to stick my neck out but
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.90,0:27:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Another hot afternoon isn't it I
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.30,0:27:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually looking for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.70,0:27:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There doctor what are you doing he's got a gun
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.10,0:27:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother and I we often used to go walking together
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.50,0:28:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,On summer afternoons a lot like this one there was a long road we took and alongside of the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.90,0:28:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Field of sunflowers but mother's dead now this is important so I need you to listen did someone ask
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.30,0:28:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To use that gun tell me was it a man was it a man it was one day
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.70,0:28:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This young man came up to me at a local bar and was he about 20 years old with blonde hair
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.33,0:28:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He was and he had a Big Bright Beautiful Smile called himself a
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.96,0:28:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's going by Eric now
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.26,0:28:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We met a few times and we eventually became very close friends
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.10,0:28:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He invited me over to the place where he was staying
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.18,0:28:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the estate of councilman Springer
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.48,0:28:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he live in that Mansion until recently
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.30,0:28:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes he did for a year in fact
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.86,0:28:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He said they took good care of him he was like a son to them
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.44,0:28:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute I had my eye on that house for a month it never saw anyone who looked like that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.30,0:28:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They were a wonderful family
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.86,0:28:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a picture
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.14,0:28:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The councilman is wife and me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.47,0:28:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.50,0:29:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something I couldn't forgive them for
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.85,0:29:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a beautiful area on their property a bit of sunflowers in their yard
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.20,0:29:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day the councilman cleared it all up in order to build a bigger driveway
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.06,0:29:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I mentioned to my young friend that I thought it was awful I was delighted to discover he agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.95,0:29:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait are you saying you actually killed them because of some flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.05,0:29:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.07,0:29:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There was more to it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.86,0:29:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He also told me councilman Springer had a mistress
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.47,0:29:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when my friend looked at me and said
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.78,0:29:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided I no longer wish to live with or be a member of the Springer household
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.90,0:29:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on I'm not a part of that family anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.99,0:29:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he proceeded to request of me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.06,0:29:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That I erase
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.86,0:29:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The family
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.93,0:29:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a mistress is so an excusable
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.49,0:29:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was someone's mistress too she was a kept woman you know
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.84,0:30:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen listen don't think about all that stuff by the way do you know where the safest in that house I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.24,0:30:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave on the second floor in the library
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.80,0:30:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.34,0:30:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to you probably shouldn't stick around here
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.99,0:30:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can erase your past did you know that if you don't like it you can erase everything
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.39,0:30:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can erase all of it and reset your entire life if you want sorry I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.79,0:30:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't agree with that at all you may try to forget but no one can simply erase their past like that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.19,0:30:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I guess you're right I wonder why I thought that it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.59,0:30:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't make any sense to me now why did I think I could erase the past by pulling the trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.99,0:30:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back I wonder why I listened to him and did what he asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.39,0:30:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should go now our talk is over I have nothing more to say
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.79,0:31:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh that's right your name is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.19,0:31:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it he left a message behind for you to make sure you take
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.59,0:31:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good look at it you'll find it in the councilman's library he predicted that you would come
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.99,0:31:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here and he was correct about that Eric also mentioned to me your fate has already been
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.39,0:31:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Decided for you so has mine
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.30,0:31:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.35,0:31:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you didn't I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.47,0:31:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you actually shoot this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.80,0:31:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh suicide I got you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.13,0:31:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.32,0:31:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the use in dying
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.62,0:31:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's over when you're dead it makes no sense
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.44,0:32:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey doctor there's nothing like living am I right you know I think I actually agree with you for a change hey what exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.84,0:32:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really do you mean for a change
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.38,0:32:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway so you're after this killer named Johanna whatever I don't get it I really don't know why you do that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.78,0:32:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey why don't you forget about this nonsense in team up with me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.87,0:32:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh by the way I don't know why but when I try to open the door to this room before it kind of gave me the cre
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.52,0:32:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter you shaking like a leaf doc
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.92,0:32:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me look at me my monster inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.32,0:33:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Johansson mrso just a game to you isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.02,0:33:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Doc wait up oh come on wait listen to me hey Doc I'm talking
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.42,0:33:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you oh for crying out loud I've got some really good news to tell you you're going to thank me for this
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.82,0:33:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll keep your promise in team up with me right I never said a team up with you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.22,0:33:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought you might need some money to run from the cops but I guess I was wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.65,0:33:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just getting the car
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.77,0:33:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our first client
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.33,0:33:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The nice man will ask her to your patient doc
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.14,0:33:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hang on to your things for now if you want them back you'd better do your job get paid
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.54,0:33:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest and meet up with me at Frank's Tavern on graston Street
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.41,0:33:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So long now get out there and earn your keep
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.81,0:34:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's what I call a profitable business
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.37,0:34:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sincerity got in advance I suppose it's time to go and have a drink
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.74,0:34:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey counselor I brought back a doctor for you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.14,0:34:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.54,0:34:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry please stop the bleeding
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.94,0:34:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears your auxiliary artery has been damaged did you get hit by a shotgun yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.74,0:34:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get that far I could not operate on you here even if I had the proper equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.14,0:34:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs to be taken to a fully equipped Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.54,0:34:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,About how long ago was he wounded can the questions doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.94,0:35:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,4 hours ago huh
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.34,0:35:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you involved in the terrorist attack this morning and what does it matter if we were
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.74,0:35:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.05,0:35:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you say
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.58,0:35:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not helping people who took others lives and discriminately you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.98,0:35:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're in right now either you help him or you die
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.29,0:35:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down Carl
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.34,0:35:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen daughter our friends will be coming to help us soon so it's simple all you need to do is stop
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.74,0:35:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The bleeding to buy me some time
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.37,0:35:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you think you're doing do you want to die I already told you to come down
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.74,0:35:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.02,0:35:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you listen to me very carefully my life is in this doctor's hands right now
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.66,0:35:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.19,0:35:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can shoot them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.50,0:36:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not running a charity here no you are so you got to pay back
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.90,0:36:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,$250,000 marks we let you simple as that auto Heckle but Mr gloss I want to pay you back
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.30,0:36:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir that's nice I'm glad you feel that way how considerate
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.39,0:36:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go on ahead and break both his arms
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.79,0:36:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it I'm getting them pay you back I will that's a good boy I just need you to give me one more month
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.19,0:36:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like both his legs too
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.34,0:36:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They are Max steindorf and Carl blunt
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.34,0:36:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute it's them I can pay you back that money I know where those guys are I really do
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.74,0:36:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll take care of what I owe you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.28,0:36:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This it better be the truth otherwise I'm going to break your scrawny necklace
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.42,0:37:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man that's right I forgot to miss
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.82,0:37:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get those guys oh well who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.46,0:37:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You called me a murderer who goes around killing people and discriminately
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.06,0:37:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you're wrong doctor what I did have meaning there was a good reason for what I did
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.72,0:37:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.00,0:37:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The president of gwe is dead I can finally die in peace
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.86,0:37:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't mind I achieved what I set out to do
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.96,0:37:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.50,0:37:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be a lawyer in East Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.06,0:37:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend here was a political secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.64,0:37:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the Wall came down
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.43,0:37:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost our jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.50,0:37:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what it is like for us after the wall felt gwe came to the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.90,0:37:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With their big funding
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.18,0:37:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They barged in and built these factories on our land
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.02,0:37:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One after another
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.07,0:37:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was our country Our Land
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.63,0:37:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They had no right to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.19,0:38:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They stepped all over our pride
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.26,0:38:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm proud to have shot that bastard
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.36,0:38:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I did it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.69,0:38:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.22,0:38:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.02,0:38:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cold
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.30,0:38:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on just hang on I'm friends will be here soon
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.62,0:38:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't come
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.95,0:38:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that our friends
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.51,0:38:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't be joining us
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.38,0:38:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the bleeding
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.17,0:38:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.45,0:38:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry I'll shoot you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.54,0:38:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it I don't want to die
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.66,0:38:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.97,0:38:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.53,0:38:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.93,0:38:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid of dying well now you know what they all felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.33,0:39:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The 12 people you killed that's how they died this is what they went through how do you know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.73,0:39:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get scissors and disinfectant
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.13,0:39:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that too much to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.53,0:39:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Arterial bleeding is pretty bad he's in a State of Shock from low blood pressure and I can keep my hand pressed against the wound
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.93,0:39:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the bleeding I'm going to have to suture the open flesh here needle and thread
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.33,0:39:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have that fine then a stapler will do what a stapler just go and get it yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.53,0:39:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.93,0:40:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What what do you think you're doing I've done what I can he needs to get to a hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.33,0:40:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What hospital no what are you thinking if
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.73,0:40:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't put him down right now I'll tell you pull the trigger if you want but if you kill me know
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.13,0:40:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes you're going to have to carry into the hospital yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.86,0:40:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down right here just save yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.78,0:40:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just realized I seen your face somewhere before you're the doctor wanted in connection with
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.18,0:40:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Serial murders aren't you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.97,0:40:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down dammit
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.58,0:41:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did this morning was not an indiscriminate attack the men I killed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.98,0:41:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The president of gwe is lackeys and his bodyguards and they all had it coming
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.86,0:41:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're telling me there were no innocent victims in that shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.98,0:41:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about that girl at the Newsstand
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.57,0:41:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You already knew about it then
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.62,0:41:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew you shot that girl didn't you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.99,0:41:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bother saving a man like me
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.32,0:41:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't because you were afraid to get shot you weren't afraid to die I could tell by the look in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.72,0:41:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did you do it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.28,0:41:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why save a terrorist like me why would you even bother
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.66,0:41:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believe in you I have faith in your Humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.57,0:41:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get going the police will be here soon
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.41,0:41:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You hang in there
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.78,0:42:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.34,0:42:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You are truly a great doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.74,0:42:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And the money what happened to the money Hey Duck don't tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.54,0:42:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Something come on without incident
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.94,0:42:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey we ain't operating no charity outfit
